#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:502
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If you have a iCalendar or vCalendar file, and you would like to import "
#| "it, choose the <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Import</"
